<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望自己去旅行會多啲信心啦"},{"pid":"5afb7ab2d46f82fbb6e50da01b0a509306f58cbe","tid":822884,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c29d25bffc9d2c9e8867bfca54f4a8f7b135f68","tid":822884,"uid":101232,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"30159e8718b92f4e7ad15578cdd448aefa0acbd0","tid":822884,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"對住一大班人完全唔識講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下自己旅行啦 但係都好似埋唔到堆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有冇巴絲可以講下成功例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"我之前試過自己一個走去報學校啲summer團 想逼下自己跳出comfort zone 系冇哂自己啲frd嘅情況下 睇下可唔可以改下內向嘅性格<br />\nPs 平時有frd就好多嗲 冇frd系到就變左啞<br />\n去完番黎之後 性格確實比以前變得yo左 因為系嗰個團如果內向唔同人講野 自己會on99企埋一邊 逼住要r下人吹水 埋堆 叫做有改善咁<br />\n但始終一個人如果本身係內向 好難一時半刻就變到外向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家睇你打篇長文出黎 就知你出去開talk都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2a35a36f5107ebcb5714dfd37a8d81f43d00cb","tid":822884